# Placement System Upgrade & TPO Role Implementation

Extend the placement module to support role-based management, dynamic data fetching, and automated statistics visualization.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Persistence (No Cloud)**: To avoid the cloud while keeping data consistent across environments (like your friend's Codespaces), we will use **Approach: Seeding Script**.
> - I will create a `seed_data.json` file in the repository.
> - I will provide a `npm run seed` command that imports this data into the local MongoDB.
> - This way, whoever clones and runs the project gets the exact same "starting" data.

> [!NOTE]
> **TPO Data Entry Options**: You mentioned CSV vs GUI. I suggest a **Hybrid Approach**:
> - **Bulk Upload (CSV)**: For importing massive "Past Offers" and "Alumni" data quickly.
> - **Live GUI (CRUD)**: For the TPO to add a "Present Drive" or edit a specific record instantly without re-uploading a file.

